<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="clarify-vt">clarify <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'klærəfaɪ/    美 /'klærəfaɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>澄清 (思想、问题等)；阐明</strong></h4>
<p>to make sth clearer and easy to understand：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>clarify one’s stand
阐明自己的立场</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You can clarify this question if you study British history.
研究一下英国历史，你就能够弄明白这个问题。</p><footer>人教⑤ – 2</footer></div></div>